{"tid":1725420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［要正視］大家一齊討論下係咪要訂啲規矩","createTime":"2019-11-15T17:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T11:07:12.000Z","uid":180442,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"93454087c31e8923660611170d2a97339c80a43f","tid":1725420,"uid":180442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"［長文］<br />\n<br />\n睇咗幾個post 唔少人話想訂啲規矩<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">呢個係唔少人嘅訴求 就算好定壞 都希望大家一齊參與討論同嘗試</span><br />\n<br />\n依家最多人討論嘅係 <span style=\"color: orange;\">鶳、裝修、火魔嘅使用</span><br />\n應該就住以上三點訂立一啲「規矩」<br />\n<br />\n好多人憂慮難以執行。有巴打提我，一直以嚟，運動都係以<span style=\"color: red;\">大家嘅共識</span>去執行<br />\n<br />\n例如<span style=\"color: gold;\">不割蓆 不篤灰</span> 係我哋靠<span style=\"color: red;\">共識</span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">成功執行</span></span>嘅<br />\n<br />\n所以，我建議好似不割蓆不篤灰咁，用口號用意識刻印落大家腦海，靠大家堅持。五個幾月以來嘅運動，唔係一直都係咁咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家對準政權、黑警。唔好再開咁多個post討論中大呢幾日嘅行為令政府成功逆轉民意</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認真傾點樣控制翻個局面好過啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住係<span style=\"color: red;\">控制</span>，唔係捉鬼，唔係篤灰，上文亦冇割蓆！<br />\n<br />\n一個人嘅腦力有限，下面開放討論，有錯請指正"},{"pid":"4d520eadf6e3646951877263e0d245ba8f738abb","tid":1725420,"uid":180442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5afc73108cbd280dad46db0b36c2e845cefbfbd6","tid":1725420,"uid":180442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:45:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0306e8ecbf26752fc6f0d703bfb6066097f0b12","tid":1725420,"uid":180442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:45:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dcf2f10b24cddb8ea7c4661cf4b03733d6351cc","tid":1725420,"uid":261812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:50:03.000Z","msg":"極讚成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.